    <section id="topics" class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-5 py-12 md:px-8 lg:px-12">
      <div class="mb-8 max-w-3xl"><p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[.25em] text-cyan-300">Topic Cluster</p><h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-black text-white md:text-5xl">按客户端和错误类型查看专题</h2><p class="mt-4 text-slate-400">首页讲完整路径，专题页提供更具体的客户端配置、错误码排查和安全清单。</p></div>
      <div class="grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">{topicLinks.map(([title, href, text]) => <a href={href} class="rounded-[1.5rem] border border-white/10 bg-slate-950/65 p-6 no-underline shadow-xl shadow-black/20 transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-cyan-300/50 hover:bg-cyan-300/10"><h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white">{title}</h3><p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-400">{text}</p><span class="mt-5 inline-flex text-sm font-bold text-cyan-200">查看专题 →</span></a>)}</div>
    </section>

    <section id="faq" class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-5 py-14 md:px-8 lg:px-12">
      <p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[.25em] text-cyan-300">FAQ</p><h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-black text-white md:text-5xl">常见问题</h2>
      <div class="mt-8 grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-2">{faq.map(([q, a]) => <div class="rounded-[1.5rem] border border-white/10 bg-white/[.045] p-6"><h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white">{q}</h3><p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-400">{a}</p></div>)}</div>
    </section>

    <section class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-5 pb-20 md:px-8 lg:px-12">
      <div class="rounded-[2rem] border border-cyan-300/20 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-300/15 via-indigo-500/10 to-slate-950 p-8 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-white md:text-5xl">下一步：选择你的客户端配置方式</h2>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-5 max-w-3xl leading-8 text-slate-300">继续查看 Claude Code、Codex、OpenAI 兼容 API、错误排查和 API Key 安全专题，按自己的客户端选择对应配置方式。</p>
        <a href="https://www.531288.xyz" class="mt-8 inline-flex rounded-full border-0 bg-cyan-300 px-7 py-3 font-black text-slate-950 no-underline shadow-xl shadow-cyan-400/25">打开中转站</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
